# Day 4 - Color Changer App

This is my Day 4 project of the 30 Days JavaScript Challenge.

## Project Description
A simple web application that allows users to change the background color of the page by clicking different buttons.

##  Features
- Change background color (Red, Green, Blue)
- Interactive UI with buttons
- Fast and responsive design
- Easy to use

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

##  Project Structure
index.html
style.css
script.js
  ## How to Use
1. Open the website
2. Click on any color button (Red, Green, Blue)
3. Background color will change instantly

